description: Demolition of existing buildings and the erection on Carnwath Road of 1 x part 4, part 5, part 6 storey building and 1 x part 1, part 5, part 6 storey building, plus basement car park and residents gym to provide 135 apartments and one single, family dwelling; and the erection on Sulivan Road of 13 x terraced, mews style houses of 3 storeys plus mansard roof; with associated car parking (140 spaces), cycle parking (172 spaces, plus 8 visitor spaces), motor cycle parking (6 spaces), landscaping and amenity space including children's play area.
